  • Field Details

    • id

      @Expose(serialize=false, deserialize=true) private int id
      The id of the instance, provided by the server. It is exposed to Gson, cannot be serialized and can be deserialized.

    • title

      @Expose private java.lang.String title
      The title of the instance. It is exposed to Gson, can be both serialized and deserialized.

    • note

      @Expose private java.lang.String note
      The note(description) of the instance. It is exposed to Gson, can be both serialized and deserialized.

    • parentId

      @Expose private int parentId
      The parent id of the instance. It is exposed to Gson, can be both serialized and deserialized.

    • existing

      private boolean existing
      The boolean to indicate whether this instance is on the server. false inidicates this instance is only existing in local storage.

    • parent

      private Node parent
      The parent object of the instance.

    • nodes

      private java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,​Node> nodes
      The children Node object of the instance.

    • TYPE_DICTIONARY

      private final java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.lang.Integer> TYPE_DICTIONARY
      The dictionary of the Node hierarchy. It is used to identify the parent or children type.

      getTypeByLevel(String, int)
